WEBVTT

00:02:34.977 --> 00:02:37.582
[NARRATOR] All pirates searching
for the treasure One Piece

00:02:37.616 --> 00:02:40.487
must brave the second half
of the Grand Line.

00:02:40.521 --> 00:02:45.732
These wild and dangerous seas
are known as the New World.

00:02:45.765 --> 00:02:48.303
Gold Roger and his crew
were the only men to ever

00:02:48.336 --> 00:02:51.543
chart these waters and
learn all the secrets they held.

00:02:51.576 --> 00:02:53.446
For the rest of the
pirates in the world,

00:02:53.479 --> 00:02:55.952
this has proven to be
the end of the road.

00:02:55.985 --> 00:02:58.791
A graveyard of dreams.

00:03:00.027 --> 00:03:03.266
[NARRATOR] Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
a boy whose body became rubber

00:03:03.299 --> 00:03:04.803
after eating the Gum Gum Fruit,

00:03:04.837 --> 00:03:08.577
sets sail into the New World
with his faithful crew.

00:03:08.611 --> 00:03:12.885
I'm gonna be the
King of the Pirates!

00:03:15.424 --> 00:03:16.960
[NARRATOR]
In order to defeat one of the

00:03:16.993 --> 00:03:18.764
Four Emperors of the New World,

00:03:18.797 --> 00:03:21.202
the Straw Hats form
an alliance with Law.

00:03:21.236 --> 00:03:23.774
Their current objective
is to destroy a man-made

00:03:23.807 --> 00:03:26.580
Devil Fruit Factory in
the kingdom of Dressrosa.

00:03:26.613 --> 00:03:29.218
In response, Doflamingo
trapped the kingdom inside

00:03:29.251 --> 00:03:31.122
a barrier known as
the "Birdcage,"

00:03:31.155 --> 00:03:33.259
and challenged all
present to a game.

00:03:33.292 --> 00:03:34.696
As the Straw Hats do battle with

00:03:34.730 --> 00:03:37.267
the fierce fighters of
the Don Quixote Family,

00:03:37.301 --> 00:03:39.405
Luffy and Law rush
to the royal palace

00:03:39.438 --> 00:03:42.812
to take down Doflamingo himself.

00:03:42.845 --> 00:03:43.948
They keep coming.

00:03:43.981 --> 00:03:46.485
Then I'll keep punching!

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:47.589
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATES gasp]

00:03:47.622 --> 00:03:49.726
[KELLY]
Hey, you buncha crap bags.

00:03:49.759 --> 00:03:52.732
Keep yer' paws off
Straw Hat or else!

00:03:52.766 --> 00:03:54.803
Rah Rah Rah Rampage!

00:03:55.505 --> 00:03:57.809
[KELLY] Anyway, I found
a shortcut you can use.

00:03:57.842 --> 00:03:59.847
Huh? Seriously?

00:03:59.880 --> 00:04:03.119
See that? Shortcut! Told ya!

00:04:03.152 --> 00:04:04.388
[LUFFY gasps]

00:04:04.421 --> 00:04:07.060
[KELLY] What're you
waiting for? Go ahead.

00:04:07.094 --> 00:04:09.332
I'll stay here and
keep watch for you.

00:04:09.365 --> 00:04:11.035
Thanks! Sounds awesome!

00:04:11.068 --> 00:04:12.672
Moocy, let's go!

00:04:12.705 --> 00:04:15.310
[BULL moos]

00:04:17.114 --> 00:04:19.085
[TRANSPONDER SNAIL A ringing]

00:04:19.118 --> 00:04:20.821
[ROBIN]
Hi, Luffy. It's me.

00:04:20.855 --> 00:04:21.890
[LUFFY]
Robin!

00:04:21.924 --> 00:04:24.763
Good news. Viola found
the key to the cuffs.

00:04:24.796 --> 00:04:25.832
Let's meet up.

00:04:25.865 --> 00:04:27.034
Oh, awesome!

00:04:27.067 --> 00:04:31.041
Luffy, we'll meet at the
Sunflower Field, that's perfect.

00:04:32.211 --> 00:04:34.749
Turn back! This place
is flooded!

00:04:38.256 --> 00:04:40.327
[LUFFY gasps]
It's a dead end!

00:04:40.360 --> 00:04:42.231
[LAW]
Get out! Hurry!

00:04:42.264 --> 00:04:44.602
[LUFFY]
Don't panic, Moocy!

00:04:53.587 --> 00:04:56.761
[DOFLAMINGO] This is nothing
but a sideways water well.

00:04:56.794 --> 00:04:59.933
More of a trap than
a shortcut, really.

00:04:59.966 --> 00:05:01.001
[gasps]

00:05:03.574 --> 00:05:07.882
[LUFFY]
It's you! Doflamingo!

00:05:15.531 --> 00:05:17.133
[LUFFY]
"A Great Escape!

00:05:17.167 --> 00:05:20.440
Luffy's Tide-turning
Elephant Gun!"

00:05:30.193 --> 00:05:34.067
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]

00:05:39.278 --> 00:05:40.815
Doflamingo!

00:05:40.848 --> 00:05:44.589
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]
Look at you two,

00:05:44.623 --> 00:05:47.662
huddled together
in your little hole.

00:05:47.695 --> 00:05:50.968
Should I take those
handcuffs off for you, Law?

00:05:51.001 --> 00:05:53.807
Or should I cut your
wrists along with them?

00:05:54.776 --> 00:05:56.547
I thought you were
at the palace--

00:05:56.580 --> 00:05:59.051
What're you doing down here?

00:06:01.890 --> 00:06:05.665
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]
I came to rescue you, of course!

00:06:05.698 --> 00:06:08.637
You clearly need help if you're
falling for traps like this.

00:06:08.670 --> 00:06:11.744
I'll put you out of your misery.

00:06:11.777 --> 00:06:13.045
Be careful!

00:06:14.348 --> 00:06:16.954
[BULL moos]

00:06:16.987 --> 00:06:17.956
[LUFFY gasps]

00:06:17.989 --> 00:06:19.892
Bullet String!

00:06:21.128 --> 00:06:24.202
[groans]

00:06:24.235 --> 00:06:25.236
Moocy!

00:06:25.270 --> 00:06:27.908
Forget the bull! Get away!

00:06:32.919 --> 00:06:35.023
[LUFFY]
Moocy!

00:06:36.926 --> 00:06:42.271
[DOFLAMINGO] Huh. No sense
of self-preservation.

00:06:42.304 --> 00:06:47.080
Don't die, Moocy. It's okay.

00:06:47.114 --> 00:06:50.353
What a joke. Look at you.

00:06:50.386 --> 00:06:53.628
Any clown could kill you
in this sorry state.

00:06:53.661 --> 00:06:56.934
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]

00:06:56.967 --> 00:06:59.639
You've riled up quite an
army of idiots out there,

00:06:59.672 --> 00:07:02.444
thinking they can take my head.

00:07:03.748 --> 00:07:07.353
[DOFLAMINGO] You are quite adept
at bringing people to your side,

00:07:07.387 --> 00:07:09.659
no matter how foolish
it may seem.

00:07:09.692 --> 00:07:11.328
I've admired that
quality of yours

00:07:11.362 --> 00:07:15.370
since I saw it on display
during the battle at Marineford.

00:07:15.403 --> 00:07:19.378
But now? I see you're
just some fool

00:07:19.411 --> 00:07:21.984
whose luck has finally run out.

00:07:22.017 --> 00:07:25.558
Why did you side
with this idiot, Law?

00:07:25.591 --> 00:07:27.094
When you were young,
I thought you showed

00:07:27.127 --> 00:07:29.532
a great deal of promise.

00:07:29.566 --> 00:07:33.306
Even as a child you were
more cunning than this,

00:07:33.339 --> 00:07:38.215
and more ruthless. Am I wrong?

00:07:39.986 --> 00:07:42.124
[DOFLAMINGO]
I'm so disappointed.

00:07:42.157 --> 00:07:45.130
Who made you into such
a miserable little coward?

00:07:45.163 --> 00:07:46.766
That's enough!

00:07:48.971 --> 00:07:50.240
Huh?

00:07:50.273 --> 00:07:51.676
You listen!

00:07:51.710 --> 00:07:54.783
I'm not gonna be like you!

00:07:54.816 --> 00:07:57.789
'Cause I... I've been saved!

00:07:57.822 --> 00:08:02.732
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles] By my dear
brother, Corazon, you mean?

00:08:03.868 --> 00:08:08.076
[DOFLAMINGO] You're worse than
a coward. You're useless.

00:08:08.109 --> 00:08:11.315
You made a choice,
not only to die in vain,

00:08:11.348 --> 00:08:14.254
but to do it alongside
this imbecile.

00:08:28.249 --> 00:08:32.190
Don't you dare! Keep your
hands off Straw Hat!

00:08:32.224 --> 00:08:34.529
Or you'll be sorry!

00:08:44.415 --> 00:08:46.687
[DOFLAMINGO chuckles]

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:48.322
[ABDULLAH, JEET gasp]

00:08:48.355 --> 00:08:49.860
What is this?

00:08:49.893 --> 00:08:51.095
It's creepy!

00:08:51.129 --> 00:08:53.701
It's not the real thing--
It's just a clone.

00:08:53.734 --> 00:08:57.040
--[JEET] Clone?
--A puppet made of string.

00:09:05.089 --> 00:09:06.325
Thanks you guys.

00:09:06.358 --> 00:09:07.528
Are you okay?

00:09:07.561 --> 00:09:08.864
Glad we came!

00:09:08.897 --> 00:09:11.837
Anyway, let's get him out
of that water already!

00:09:11.870 --> 00:09:12.938
Right!

00:09:13.707 --> 00:09:16.713
[JEET] You're not hurt
too bad, are you?

00:09:23.627 --> 00:09:25.898
[TOWNSMAN A gasps]
Stay back!

00:09:33.647 --> 00:09:35.617
Doflamingo!

00:09:37.121 --> 00:09:41.930
[chuckles] That's one hundred
million berries, just for me.

00:09:41.964 --> 00:09:45.203
A free ticket to join
the Don Quixote Family,

00:09:45.237 --> 00:09:46.940
right in my sights!

00:09:46.974 --> 00:09:48.243
[gunshot]

00:09:48.276 --> 00:09:52.250
[gasping] Who's there?

00:09:54.054 --> 00:09:58.095
[BOUNTY HUNTER A] Damn it!
Go away! You old fart!

00:09:58.831 --> 00:10:01.168
This is not your kingdom!

00:10:01.202 --> 00:10:03.272
I won't let you kill him!

00:10:03.306 --> 00:10:05.577
Get out of here,
you damn pirate!

00:10:05.611 --> 00:10:08.116
Screw you!

00:10:08.149 --> 00:10:09.484
Wanna stand in my way?

00:10:09.519 --> 00:10:11.690
I'll shoot you, too!

00:10:11.723 --> 00:10:13.627
[KYROS grunts]

00:10:19.873 --> 00:10:22.177
Nice work. You saved me.

00:10:22.211 --> 00:10:25.316
Truly, sir. I'm grateful.

00:10:32.832 --> 00:10:36.773
[TOWNSMAN B]
I... I'm begging you.

00:10:36.807 --> 00:10:38.644
Please. Stand down.

00:10:38.677 --> 00:10:42.350
Surrender! Let me take you in!

00:10:47.261 --> 00:10:49.832
Forgive me, but I cannot.

00:10:51.002 --> 00:10:52.771
Stay back!

00:10:52.805 --> 00:10:54.709
I know that you
don't want to fight.

00:10:54.742 --> 00:10:57.347
That this kingdom
longs for peace.

00:10:58.283 --> 00:11:00.921
[KYROS] Doflamingo is
forcing this madness on you.

00:11:00.954 --> 00:11:04.963
And for that crime, he will pay.

00:11:04.996 --> 00:11:07.066
[gasps]

00:11:10.206 --> 00:11:11.408
Don't give up.

00:11:15.016 --> 00:11:19.659
Ugh. You saved me. Thank you.

00:11:19.692 --> 00:11:21.395
[JEET]
Aw, it was nuthin'!

00:11:21.429 --> 00:11:23.700
One question. Did we win?

00:11:23.734 --> 00:11:25.203
He's just legs now.

00:11:25.236 --> 00:11:28.276
That's the guy we were supposed
to fight at the palace, right?

00:11:28.309 --> 00:11:30.380
Moron! I just told you!

00:11:30.413 --> 00:11:31.916
It's only his puppet!

00:11:31.950 --> 00:11:33.319
Though I don't know
why he bothered

00:11:33.352 --> 00:11:34.989
to send one all the way here.

00:11:35.023 --> 00:11:37.060
Does he want to
taunt us that badly?

00:11:37.093 --> 00:11:39.364
[LUFFY]
He said he was gonna rescue us.

00:11:39.398 --> 00:11:41.536
Oh! That reminds me!

00:11:41.569 --> 00:11:43.105
That Kelly Funk guy from before.

00:11:43.138 --> 00:11:47.480
He tricked us! Everything
that bastard said was a lie!

00:11:51.322 --> 00:11:52.959
Kid's a real sucker.

00:11:52.992 --> 00:11:55.429
He walked straight
into that one.

00:11:58.069 --> 00:11:59.940
[JEET] After we learned
what he was plotting,

00:11:59.973 --> 00:12:02.845
we knew we had to stop him!

00:12:02.879 --> 00:12:06.786
Straw Hat needs our help!
Get up, Abdullah!

00:12:07.855 --> 00:12:09.859
[BOTH gasp]

00:12:09.892 --> 00:12:11.094
[KELLY gasps]

00:12:15.904 --> 00:12:17.608
[JEET]
Kelly's a famous assassin

00:12:17.642 --> 00:12:20.815
and he cut him down
in a split second!

00:12:20.848 --> 00:12:23.185
Aw man, that's not fair!

00:12:23.219 --> 00:12:24.789
Mingo did rescue me!

00:12:24.823 --> 00:12:28.597
Traffy's right!
He's laughing at us!

00:12:28.631 --> 00:12:30.967
How's Cabbage doing?
Is he beating us?

00:12:31.001 --> 00:12:34.307
[JEET] Yeah, we're falling
way behind. It's been a while.

00:12:34.341 --> 00:12:36.478
Everyone might be
on the second level.

00:12:36.513 --> 00:12:39.820
[LUFFY groans] We gotta get
to the Sunflower Field--

00:12:39.853 --> 00:12:41.557
I needed that shortcut!

00:12:41.590 --> 00:12:43.660
Hurry back to the entrance!

00:12:43.693 --> 00:12:45.965
--[LUFFY] No.
--Huh?

00:12:45.998 --> 00:12:49.237
I'll make us a shortcut.
Just watch me.

00:12:49.270 --> 00:12:50.106
[BOTH]
Huh?

00:12:50.139 --> 00:12:51.208
What're you--

00:12:51.241 --> 00:12:55.417
All we gotta do is go up.
That's easy enough!

00:12:55.450 --> 00:12:58.857
[ABDULLAH, JEET scream]

00:13:02.097 --> 00:13:03.198
What?

00:13:05.470 --> 00:13:08.510
[KYROS] Everyone must've reached
the second level already.

00:13:10.413 --> 00:13:11.549
Better hurry.

00:13:11.583 --> 00:13:14.955
[JEET] Wait! Think this through
a second, Straw Hat!

00:13:15.958 --> 00:13:17.393
Straw Hat's here?

00:13:17.427 --> 00:13:19.766
[LUFFY]
Gum-Gum...

00:13:19.799 --> 00:13:21.769
[ABDULLAH, JEET scream]

00:13:21.803 --> 00:13:27.180
Ahh! All those losers made it
up to the second level already!

00:13:27.213 --> 00:13:29.250
That's crazy!

00:13:35.096 --> 00:13:38.102
[MACHVISE]
Our underl-eens are lose-een.

00:13:38.136 --> 00:13:41.008
I don't see Straw Hat
or his crew out there.

00:13:41.041 --> 00:13:43.847
Let's start picking
them off, one by one.

00:13:43.880 --> 00:13:45.584
Works for me!

00:13:46.987 --> 00:13:50.961
[CAVENDISH gasps]
What's wrong, Farul?

00:13:51.830 --> 00:13:53.733
Uh-oh.

00:13:53.767 --> 00:13:55.570
What's that racket?

00:14:00.781 --> 00:14:02.685
There's something big coming up!

00:14:02.718 --> 00:14:08.062
[LUFFY yelling]

00:14:08.096 --> 00:14:12.403
...Elephant Gun! Let's go!

00:14:33.479 --> 00:14:37.487
...Elephant Gun! Let's go!

00:14:42.097 --> 00:14:46.238
[CAVENDISH] What is that?
Someone's fist?

00:14:46.271 --> 00:14:47.373
Well, damn.

00:14:47.406 --> 00:14:51.248
[CHIN JAO chuckles]
That's rather clever of you!

00:14:51.281 --> 00:14:55.089
I'd expect no less
from Garp's grandson.

00:14:55.123 --> 00:14:56.225
Ooh!

00:14:56.258 --> 00:14:59.063
That must be Straw Hat's doing.

00:15:00.668 --> 00:15:02.470
[DELLINGER squeals]

00:15:04.141 --> 00:15:06.445
[DELLINGER]
Incoming!

00:15:12.624 --> 00:15:14.695
[GLADIUS]
Straw Hat!

00:15:14.729 --> 00:15:18.335
[laughs] I'm enjoying
this chaos!

00:15:18.369 --> 00:15:19.237
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATE A]
Chin Jao and the others are

00:15:19.271 --> 00:15:20.306
headed to the third level!

00:15:20.339 --> 00:15:22.377
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATE B]
Stop them!

00:15:22.410 --> 00:15:24.582
What was all that
rumbling about?

00:15:24.615 --> 00:15:25.584
Aw crap.

00:15:25.618 --> 00:15:27.554
It's coming our way!

00:15:28.322 --> 00:15:29.826
[GLADIUS]
You don't even know what it is!

00:15:29.859 --> 00:15:31.596
You have no right to be scared!

00:15:31.630 --> 00:15:34.702
You keep fighting--
Don't lose sight of the enemy!

00:15:38.710 --> 00:15:40.279
Stay focused!

00:15:46.325 --> 00:15:49.532
All right! Traffy. Let's go!

00:15:49.565 --> 00:15:52.538
[JEET, ABDULLAH] He made
a shortcut with his fist!

00:15:52.572 --> 00:15:53.940
We could've been crushed!

00:15:53.974 --> 00:15:56.680
Hey, guys! You take care
of Moocy for me, okay?

00:15:56.713 --> 00:15:57.615
[ABDULLAH, JEET]
Yessir!

00:15:57.649 --> 00:16:00.352
All right! Up we go!

00:16:01.254 --> 00:16:02.858
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATE F]
What happened?

00:16:02.891 --> 00:16:06.231
That hole,
it came outta nowhere!

00:16:07.868 --> 00:16:09.337
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATE G gasps]

00:16:13.379 --> 00:16:14.883
A hand?

00:16:14.916 --> 00:16:21.228
[LUFFY]
Gum-Gum... Rocket!

00:16:21.261 --> 00:16:23.332
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATES scream]

00:16:25.036 --> 00:16:28.075
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATES]
It's Straw Hat!

00:16:34.622 --> 00:16:38.328
Good! Now we're caught
up with everyone else!

00:16:38.362 --> 00:16:39.164
Get ready!

00:16:39.197 --> 00:16:41.536
Is that Law I see?

00:16:43.773 --> 00:16:45.476
What's the hold up? Move it!

00:16:45.510 --> 00:16:50.386
All right. I'm comin'
for you, Mingo!

00:17:18.776 --> 00:17:20.379
That's heavy!

00:17:25.557 --> 00:17:30.533
Dragon Claw Fist!
Dragon... Claw!

00:17:33.773 --> 00:17:36.177
This is one hell of a fight!

00:17:48.168 --> 00:17:50.006
I should've known better, huh?

00:17:50.039 --> 00:17:52.143
I can't use smoke
to distract you.

00:17:52.177 --> 00:17:54.180
So it would appear.

00:17:56.619 --> 00:17:58.356
The future of the
Revolutionary Army

00:17:58.389 --> 00:18:01.395
is looking quite promising
with you around.

00:18:01.428 --> 00:18:03.967
A formidable threat indeed.

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:06.772
Yeah? I question your sincerity.

00:18:23.807 --> 00:18:26.846
Fraland, we're here!

00:18:26.880 --> 00:18:29.184
Huh? What's up, you guys?

00:18:29.217 --> 00:18:31.455
We can help! Listen up!

00:18:31.488 --> 00:18:35.196
I've got a plan that'll get
the door to the factory open!

00:18:35.229 --> 00:18:36.666
Wha? Really?

00:18:36.699 --> 00:18:39.939
[INHEL] Definitely! Just keep
fighting SeÃ±or for now.

00:18:39.972 --> 00:18:42.443
We need time to pull this off!

00:18:43.345 --> 00:18:49.525
Easy peasy! You can count on me!

00:18:52.363 --> 00:18:55.771
Up there! I see two people
with one-star prizes!

00:18:55.804 --> 00:18:57.406
Fire!

00:18:59.278 --> 00:19:01.214
Not good. We've been seen.

00:19:01.247 --> 00:19:02.551
Hey, jackass!

00:19:02.585 --> 00:19:05.323
If you hit Miss Robin,
you're gonna be sorry.

00:19:05.356 --> 00:19:07.226
Don't you worry one bit!

00:19:07.259 --> 00:19:10.166
I'll put up a nice
barrier for you!

00:19:10.199 --> 00:19:12.904
Barrier time!

00:19:14.107 --> 00:19:16.211
[gasps] Aw crap!

00:19:16.245 --> 00:19:19.519
I can't cross my fingers
or I'll fall to the ground!

00:19:19.552 --> 00:19:20.955
We got this!

00:19:20.988 --> 00:19:23.225
Cut that out! Damn it!

00:19:23.258 --> 00:19:25.029
Don't make me come down there!

00:19:25.062 --> 00:19:26.566
Oh, I know!

00:19:26.599 --> 00:19:28.402
How 'bout I cause
a "rain of terror"

00:19:28.435 --> 00:19:31.041
like I did at the Coliseum?

00:19:31.075 --> 00:19:33.312
[BARTOLOMEO laughs]

00:19:33.345 --> 00:19:36.586
Huh? Wait a second!
What the hell's he doing?

00:19:36.619 --> 00:19:40.960
Huh? No way. He...
He wouldn't dare, would he?

00:19:42.397 --> 00:19:46.739
[BARTOLOMEO chuckles]
You want some of this?

00:19:46.773 --> 00:19:49.611
[BARTOLOMEO laughs]

00:19:50.479 --> 00:19:53.886
Ha! Can't take the heat, huh?

00:20:17.835 --> 00:20:20.473
[BELLAMY] So, I just gotta
win the tournament?

00:20:20.507 --> 00:20:23.546
Then you'll give me
a spot in the Family?

00:20:23.580 --> 00:20:25.583
[DOFLAMINGO]
Of course.

00:20:27.053 --> 00:20:29.659
I'll be cheering for you.

00:20:29.692 --> 00:20:33.867
[DELLINGER] I'm gonna finish
you off, right here, right now.

00:20:33.900 --> 00:20:35.837
Young Master says!

00:20:36.639 --> 00:20:38.810
[BELLAMY]
I can't go on like this.

00:20:38.843 --> 00:20:41.481
I have to settle things!

00:20:54.307 --> 00:20:55.844
[TREBOL]
Hey, hey, Doffy.

00:20:55.877 --> 00:20:58.916
Did you send String-Joker
off somewhere?

00:21:00.954 --> 00:21:03.960
[DOFLAMINGO] Yeah. I was
gonna deliver something,

00:21:03.993 --> 00:21:06.532
but I guess he doesn't need it.

00:21:06.566 --> 00:21:09.103
"Deliver something," huh?

00:21:09.939 --> 00:21:12.410
[DOFLAMINGO] While we're
sitting here waiting,

00:21:12.443 --> 00:21:15.349
do you remember the day
when Law first showed up?

00:21:15.383 --> 00:21:17.588
All those years ago?

00:21:18.489 --> 00:21:23.533
[laughs] He was crazy!
Had a wild look in his eyes!

00:21:23.566 --> 00:21:26.705
Yeah, uh-huh! [laughs]

00:21:27.473 --> 00:21:29.110
[DOFLAMINGO]
Reminded me of myself

00:21:29.144 --> 00:21:31.816
when I was that age,
to be honest.

00:21:32.818 --> 00:21:36.391
I thought "in ten years,
this hateful little monster

00:21:36.425 --> 00:21:39.363
will make a fine
right-hand-man."

00:21:42.605 --> 00:21:46.178
But now, it looks like
I'll be killing him instead.

00:21:46.211 --> 00:21:47.981
Such a pity.

00:22:02.911 --> 00:22:04.614
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATE J]
We have an intruder!

00:22:04.648 --> 00:22:06.586
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATE K] Don't
touch him! He has explosives

00:22:06.619 --> 00:22:08.055
strapped to his body!

00:22:08.088 --> 00:22:10.994
[DON QUIXOTE PIRATES scream]

00:22:11.027 --> 00:22:13.567
[DOFLAMINGO]
Hey! Who the hell is this kid?

00:22:13.600 --> 00:22:15.469
Why did you let him in?

00:22:17.439 --> 00:22:20.647
Let me join your pirate crew.

00:22:20.681 --> 00:22:21.816
Huh?

00:22:22.584 --> 00:22:25.791
I wanna destroy
everything that I see!

00:22:25.824 --> 00:22:31.301
People. Towns. I wanna burn
this whole world to the ground.

00:22:31.334 --> 00:22:34.742
You know, I'm from Flevence.

00:22:34.775 --> 00:22:37.112
I came here from the White Town.

00:22:42.991 --> 00:22:47.734
[LAW] It won't be long...
before I'm dead.

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:07.439
[LUFFY yelling]
Mingo!

00:23:14.621 --> 00:23:16.926
[NARRATOR] The Executives
of the Don Quixote Family

00:23:16.959 --> 00:23:18.195
finally enter the fray,

00:23:18.228 --> 00:23:21.669
starting a full-scale battle
with Luffy and the others.

00:23:21.702 --> 00:23:23.973
When it seems like
the palace is out of reach,

00:23:24.006 --> 00:23:26.879
the ragtag group of allies
that Luffy has acquired

00:23:26.912 --> 00:23:29.818
come together and
prove their worth!

00:23:29.852 --> 00:23:31.789
[LUFFY]
On the next One Piece!

00:23:31.822 --> 00:23:33.358
"A United Front!

00:23:33.392 --> 00:23:35.697
Luffy's Breakthrough
to the Victory!"

00:23:35.730 --> 00:23:38.736
I'm gonna be
King of the Pirates!

